ments\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"late March\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC's Future Host Commission will travel to Salt Lake City between April 9 and 13 to evaluate venues and preparations for the Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2247, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6283115251200655e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6334594701258541, \"rank\": 0.5786329613658141, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will report what they see to the Executive Board, which will decide if the bid should be put to a vote by the full membership.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Executive Board\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"the bid\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a vote\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the full membership\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We think we will blow them away.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very, very pleased with what we have to offer,\\\" Bullock said.\", \"from\": 2557, \